high_descs: Walk up to the sink.
Pick up the knife from the sink.
Turn around and walk to the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator and cut the head of lettuce inside.
Walk back to the sink.
Set the knife down in the sink.
Turn around and walk to the refrigerator again.
Pick up a slice of lettuce from the refrigerator.
Turn left and walk to the stove.
Put the lettuce slice in the pot on the stove.
Pick up the pot from the stove.
Turn left and walk to the sink.
Put the pot with the lettuce slice in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a lettuce slice in a pot in the sink.
